                {{ components.captionHeading(text='Start your Equality, Diversity and Inclusion (EDI) profile survey', tag='h2', size='m') }}

                <p class="govuk-body">To help UKRI identify inequalities in certain groups, and ensure we reach a representative section of society, we need to ask you 7 questions. Some of which you may feel are not important or relevant. However, they are to someone with that characteristic.</p>
                <p class="govuk-body">Rest assured, your answers are separated from the selection process and have no bearing on decisions made in respect of fundingapplications. Moreover, the information provided is:</p>
